<template>
  <Coin />
</template>

<script>
import  { tenCoins, matchedNames, search } from '../components/coin/Coin.js'
import '../components/coin/Coin.css'

export default {
  components: {
    Coin :{
      setup() {
        const coins = ref(tenCoins)
        const searchQuery = ref('')
        const matchedCoins = computed(() => {
          return search(coins.value, searchQuery.value)
        })
        return { coins, searchQuery, matchedCoins }
      },
    }
  }
}
</script>
